1. Install Git in your local : https://git-scm.com/download/win
 
2. Open command window and make sure Git is installed
  $ git version
    git version 2.22.0.windows.1
   
3. Set user name:
Saranraj@SGZ-IN01074 C:\Users\Saranraj
$ git config --global user.name "Saranraj Santhanam"

Saranraj@SGZ-IN01074 C:\Users\Saranraj
$ git config --global user.name
Saranraj Santhanam
  
4. Set user email:
Saranraj@SGZ-IN01074 C:\Users\Saranraj
$ git config --global user.email "saranraj.santhanam@saggezza.com"

Saranraj@SGZ-IN01074 C:\Users\Saranraj
$ git config --global user.email
saranraj.santhanam@saggezza.com
